creator: Grow Maple Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Parenting is hard. You deserve an app that helps make parenting together easier.

Meet Maple, the family app for managing your household needs. Maple’s free app helps parents collaborate on household topics, stay organized around events with a family calendar, share the workload through tasks and celebrate working better together.


Maple is the best way to parent together.

App Features and Benefits:

Maple brings your family into one place to manage the load together. App features and benefits include:

Come together as one: Invite your family to Maple to work as a team around running your household.

Family Overview: A snapshot of your household’s activities to share the load and offer help.

Household topics: Keep your family organized in topics where everyone can communicate and stay on the same page around what needs to happen.

Quality Partners: Get in-app access to dozens of brands, such as TaskRabbit and Yumi to help you take care of your tasks faster.

Family Calendar: Connect your family and/or work calendar to get everything in one place. Maple also supports connecting your Google Calendar.

Don’t let the hard work go unnoticed: Maple provides daily messages on your family’s workload and commitments, and ends the day on what’s been accomplished as a team. Be sure to take a moment to recognize the daily effort your family makes, and celebrate the hard work of managing your household.

With Maple, you’ll stop managing your family alone. Download Maple and come together.

Learn more about Maple...

Maple is a family technology company founded in 2020. Maple's mission is to improve the quality of life for families. Join us as we shape the future of parenting. Visit our website: www.growmaple.com

title: Maple - Household Planner

creator: Grow Maple Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Managing a family can leave you feeling scattered. Maple is designed to help you keep it together.

From household chores to food & meal prep, kids activities to planning your next trip, Maple’s free household management app has everything you need to stay organized, all in one place. Family organization has never been easier— stay on top of your family’s busy schedule with Maple.

Key Features:

Organize with Folders:
Maple Folders are a powerful way to keep it all together. Organize household needs with collaborative folders, customizable tooling and color coding. Invite household members or collaborators so everyone stays on top of what needs to get done and can work together.

Work from scratch or use suggested folders:
With Maple, you can create an infinite number of folders that satisfy everything you need to get organized. Additionally, Maple comes preloaded with ten folders that include tooling to get you started.

Notes:
Maple Notes allow you to write down and keep track of important family information, ideas, and documents— quickly and conveniently. Notes include a full-text editor. Organize effortlessly and ensure you never misplace information.

To-do Lists:
Stay on top of your to-do’s with Maple’s intuitive To-do List tool. Create multiple lists for different categories, prioritize items, set due dates, assign to-do’s, and even add details within a to-do in order to keep your responsibilities well-structured and manageable. Maple’s “all to-do” tab will give you clear insight on what needs to happen for your household today, this week, next and what is even overdue- nothing will sleep between the cracks with Maple.

Checklists:
Whether it's for your weekly chores, a packing list, or event preparations, Maple’s Checklists feature enables you to create detailed lists and check off items as you complete them. Say goodbye to forgotten tasks and hello to a more efficient routine.

Shopping Lists:
Make grocery shopping simple with our dedicated Shopping Lists tool. Create personalized shopping lists, quickly add specific items while Maple categorizes them by sections of the store, and easily share them with your family members or collaborators for convenience.

Event Lists:
Keep track of important dates, appointments, and gatherings with our Event List feature. Not only can you create events, set reminders, invite participants, and 2-way sync Maple’s Calendar with Google Calendar, you can also view all the events within that folder in one, easy-to-read list.

Sub-Folders:
Further organize your notes, lists, and events with Maple Sub Folders. Create subfolders within each category, allowing you to categorize and access your information more efficiently. This creates a well-structured digital environment for all your household needs.

Chat:
Collaborate and communicate seamlessly with your household members or friends using our built-in Chat feature. Share updates, discuss tasks, drop images, documents and links— and keep everyone in the loop.

About Maple:
Maple is a family technology company founded in 2020. Maple's mission is to improve the quality of life for families. Visit our website: www.growmaple.com

Organize with Folders:

Work from scratch or use suggested folders:

Meal Planner:

Recipe Box:
Maple’s recipe box allows you to easily save and organize your favorite recipes in one place. Browse the web for recipes your family loves and automatically import and store those recipes inside your Recipe Box. Quickly add recipes to your Maple Meal Planner, and view ingredients and step-by-step cooking directions.


Shopping Lists:
Make grocery shopping simple with our dedicated Shopping Lists tool. Create personalized shopping lists, quickly add specific items while Maple categorizes them by sections of the store, and easily share them with your family members or collaborators for convenience.

Notes:
Maple Notes allow you to write down and keep track of important family information, ideas, and documents— quickly and conveniently. Notes include a full-text editor. Organize effortlessly and ensure you never misplace information.

Create multiple lists for different categories, prioritize items, set due dates, assign to-do’s, and even add details within a to-do in order to keep your responsibilities well-structured and manageable. Maple’s “all to-do” tab will give you clear insight on what needs to happen for your household today, this week, next and what is even overdue- nothing will sleep between the cracks with Maple.

Whether it's for your weekly chores, a packing list, or event preparations, Maple’s Checklists feature enables you to create detailed lists and check off items as you complete them. Say goodbye to forgotten tasks and hello to a more efficient routine.

Event Lists:

Further organize your notes, lists, and events with Maple Sub Folders. Create subfolders within each category, allowing you to categorize and access your information more efficiently. This creates a well-structured digital environment for all your household needs.

Collaborate and communicate seamlessly with your household members or friends using our built-in Chat feature. Share updates, discuss tasks, drop images, documents and links— and keep everyone in the loop.
